 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Hierdie oats-en-piesangmuffins is &#8216;n absolute wenner. Maak dit voor die tyd. Dit kan tot vir &#8216;n week in &#8216;n <em>tupperware</em>-houer in die yskas hou. Haal net soggens een uit, sit dit in die mikrogolf en maak dit warm. Oatspap en piesangs was nog nooit so lekker nie. </p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-768x1024.jpg\" alt class=\"wp-image-6258\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2021/07/IMG_2717-2.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"></figure></div>",
